    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013080/extras/04830376d71ae50fb87302f391a818b6.poster.avif?t=1765365910\" width=700 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013080/extras/04830376d71ae50fb87302f391a818b6.webm?t=1765365910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013080/extras/04830376d71ae50fb87302f391a818b6.mp4?t=1765365910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ARKHAM MYSTERIES: CHAPTER ONE</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>发现那些不应被揭示的秘密</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在一场充满神秘与探索的叙事冒险中，每一次发现都将你带向真相……或是毁灭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013080/extras/1b960d81a2f729682b3a1237284c8111.avif?t=1765365910\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013080/extras_big/1b960d81a2f729682b3a1237284c8111.avif?t=1765365910 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为侦探 John Graves，你将在神秘的 Samantha Damasco 的引导下，追踪失踪的教授 Wellington。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013080/extras/397e1cd96e4bcc47cd6bcd7f8595b0f4.poster.avif?t=1765365910\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013080/extras/397e1cd96e4bcc47cd6bcd7f8595b0f4.webm?t=1765365910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013080/extras/397e1cd96e4bcc47cd6bcd7f8595b0f4.mp4?t=1765365910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>唯有卡达斯之眼能揭示隐匿之物。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索隐藏的维度，解开谜团，同时未知的力量在黑暗中潜伏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013080/extras/966d38460513401d22772b10027d44e0.poster.avif?t=1765365910\" width=700 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013080/extras/966d38460513401d22772b10027d44e0.webm?t=1765365910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013080/extras/966d38460513401d22772b10027d44e0.mp4?t=1765365910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色与游戏玩法：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第一人称探索</strong>：沉浸在充满神秘的黑暗世界中。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多重结局</strong>：每一个决定都会影响游戏的最终走向。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>维度旅行</strong>：使用卡达斯之眼揭开隐藏现实中的秘密。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神秘谜题</strong>：考验你的逻辑和智慧，解开隐藏的难题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>克苏鲁风格的怪物</strong>：运用你的智慧，在宇宙恐怖中生存。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>笼罩在黑暗中的案件</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>以侦探 John Graves 的身份，你将深入一个逻辑与理智逐渐消散的谜团。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神秘歌手 Samantha Damasco 委托你寻找失踪的教授 Wellington，他的失踪与那些不应被揭开的古老秘密紧密相连。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>凭借 Ojo de Kadath 的力量，你将跨越不可能的界限，揭示潜伏在现实之外的恐怖存在。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>某些答案需要付出代价……你愿意承担吗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
